title: ETH v1 Listing: Edit CF of MIM market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to edit previous vote to list MIM on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1. We will edit Collateral Factor.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Improve previous MIM vote https://listing.cream.finance/#/proposal/QmbwGGjSXYKH4UYdtte4CUasuj2ysRdocbruFEmUYjB1hJ

For:

Add MIM market with Collateral Factor: 75% and Collateral Cap: $50M

Against:

Leave previous MIM vote as is (https://listing.cream.finance/#/proposal/QmbwGGjSXYKH4UYdtte4CUasuj2ysRdocbruFEmUYjB1hJ).
